title: Cold War Kids - Up In Rags [2006 - EP]
description:
Up in Rags is the third EP by indie rock band from California, Cold War Kids. All the songs from this EP are contained in Cold War Kids&#039; debut album "Robbers & Cowards" which was featured in Q&#039;s top 50 albums of 2007 on #21. The song "Hang Me Up To Dry" was released as a single and ended up on #26 Billboards&#039; Hot Modern Rock Tracks list.
